name: A Bit of Nature
description:
Just a very old photo that I took some years ago, when I used to "work" as a makeup artist here and there. I'm still in love with the pic and the incredibly comfy and quiet place, so I thought that it would be nice to share it with all my NFT holders. Would like to take more photos like this more often...

Yup, I know this is not any drawing/animation (sorry), but will try my best to come back with fresh new art this 2022. Thank you all so much for your support~
